	<meta name="description" content="AdeptDC offers DataCOOL - a proprietary software appliance to enable workload-proportional cooling (i.e. cooling  in sync with IT workload) in data centers. The workload-proportional cooling is achieved by sensing IT component temperatures, using  real-time analytics to determine actual optimal cooling set-points, and automating optimal cooling by linking set-points to the building management system (BMS). The benefits from the technology are cooling cost-savings without risk of service interruption and performance degradation, improvement of cooling utilization, higher cooling equipment life, and lower maintenance cost." />
